{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2018Mistified\u2019 is the debut game from SpiceBound Studios. A fiendishly tricksy grid based puzzle game where your presence in a strange land will guide the lost souls of creatures to a better place, or a worse one. Their fate is decided by your success or failure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/Bunny_6.png?t=1734034066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve 150+ expertly designed puzzles and dig deeper to uncover further challenges that will keep you puzzling as you forge ahead throughout this charming 2D world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse the world map by manipulating the Giant Maps pet rabbit</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use sounds, such as your own footsteps, to guide creatures out of harm's way and into salvation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/Animal_Run.gif?t=1734034066\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make use of the spirit mist to transport objects or alter its path to change the direction of the flow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stomp down the dark claws to clear out a safe route.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a select bunch of handcrafted songs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">150+ Puzzles using a combination of:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 different animals, each with their own reactions and interactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 different types of log, from standard to polarising.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A HAND-full of traps that want to eat the souls of the lost and occasionally lend a helping HAND.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rivers, and their many PITfalls and uses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And much more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338020/extras/Mist_Crow.gif?t=1734034066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join our Community to stay up to date with news and puzzles!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Look out!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338020/f56e8a35af26cd020ba85fa897d6f856349c4f17.jpg"},{"name":"Culinary Endeavours","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338020/3fce2e8a6b567889e200d6e69a93d01726f893f0.jpg"},{"name":"Crowtography","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338020/f4b251a76d46aebd9689e32ff37e713e955b3355.jpg"},{"name":"Land Ho!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338020/99db54bf72ee6d1a2f95afedd82ca73213d68740.jpg"},{"name":"Open the Gates","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338020/c5faf4eb6aa6f06ed51e70dd667eeb8fd21b46a0.jpg"},{"name":"Open the Gates Home","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338020/f681524f60bb24428fad7d9f2a00ea9e005cce1f.jpg"},{"name":"Bulls 101","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338020/e65380b253448b65c4d8d9c2bae7140cb24f7bef.jpg"},{"name":"Now we are getting somewhere!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2338020/4aba6817dfb813b694eb3e12f3d73d5d4bfe4264.jpg"},{"name":"Base Camp","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/233802